Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aloha～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:56.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：aloha為夏威夷土著人的問候語）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家的禮物夏威夷果巧克力已經平安到達了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還有SOKOICHIGO的手機掛件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在夏威夷也有SOKOICHIGO…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我知錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.63,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆简体}夏天的結束(byebye)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假就要  結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業都有  好好做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  Fight  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快來看  快來看  這片沙灘真是好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  果然沒人在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本以為很長的暑假都… 真是光陰似箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦碰了面  果不其然又轉換到了遊玩模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來  第一學期的休學式上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在一個月後  9月1日再見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:40.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}9月1日聖櫻學園祭網\N直臨決戰最終更新版本大公開！\N前夜祭活動內容發表！\N新遊戲！\N全體學生參加計劃開始！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待度好高啊  但只有一個月的時間嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該是這樣的  可…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰說甚麼小意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己  你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點起來  睡著了會掛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經這樣過了兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你們停一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼章魚是蟲字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日語「章魚」漢字也寫作「蛸」）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個算蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼青魚不加魚字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把青魚當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到件好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來變換一下房間佈局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大躍進！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了佈局的話  一定能萬事OK的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個辦法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子挪個位置甚麼的就能大躍進了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  你們不覺得這裡空出來超不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就風水學來說  α波也噴湧而出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（α波：即Alpha波，8—14赫茲，精神集中時，冥想狀態亦是此種狀態。\N靈感或自覺敏銳，腦的活動活躍。）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  一切都能順利無阻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也只有這個辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小矮人先生你也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  是吧  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前衝～向前衝～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學美壞掉了  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來  睡著了會掛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該醒過來的…是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  快想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情推給別人真不像個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法…小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視嗎  又無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前衝～向前衝～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是個大男人還穿著裙子  不害臊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  不要脫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你以為這樣能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起學姐  我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是你給我上了一課才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我說一句行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們忘記了一件很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我說咯  暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這樣下去大家都會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  都會死蹺蹺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  所以我提議大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  輪流休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在喜歡的地方寫上名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來也很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看快看  這間餐廳的東西真的很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  就是暑假的最後一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來之後  我就一個人站在陌生的馬路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然拼命找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻從哪裡都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉幸福的模樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底夢到甚麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼讓她再躺一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點睡著了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這不就是你一直想買的那件T恤嘛  買下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用上個月的工資買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊  我也不要讀書算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～出社會上班真的很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都像趕廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是聖櫻坂站  聖櫻坂站到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  應該是這個吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是重新看起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美最喜歡吃抹茶紅豆冰了  她一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子學姐真是一個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶紅豆冰最棒  我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的慰問品  多佳子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼  我看了聖櫻網的營運日誌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你們好象一直住在學校的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為謝禮  就讓你欣賞一下夏威夷的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的海灘和餐廳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸的學生會長大人今天是來偵查的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是我一個人在說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又是我在自說自話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是聖櫻網的管理員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事想和學美同學談一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要在這裡做一個很大很大的門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為材料是在建材超市統一訂購的  稍微便宜了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們預定在那裡放置食品攤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那邊有烤栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是2-C的羽田她們的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是1-B的美和的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有2-D的山本她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊則是新城她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上還有工藤  渡邊還有澤村她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你全都記住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是各個店鋪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳給我們點了一把火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們每天都很愉快  這都是虧了多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再帶你逛逛那邊  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合併？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說是吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生數量不斷減少  經營停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時代還是這麼漫不經心的話  會變成這樣也不奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是保留聖櫻的名字之類的細節還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之聖櫻學園將會被我們愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸學園合併吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和聖櫻學生會長有私交不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這有甚麼關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們打算中止學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個正是聖櫻學園愚昧的經營的縮影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純的一時興起  只在乎眼前的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個完全沒有意義的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太突然了  至少等到明年…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們還處在計劃階段  應該沒有任何實際損失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大量學生  為了追求更有趣的生活而離開學校的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然選擇學生的身份的你們現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉辦這種單純的慶典究竟有甚麼意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個消息預定在九月一日公佈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前請準備好學生會長的發言稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  這個情報絕對不能外流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原同學  輸入的資料有很明顯的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意準確性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久之前就對學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐這個騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…  騙子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有辦法招待你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美同學你們為甚麼這麼拼命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是因為很愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要做很多的準備嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話大家看到這個就會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽真是害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…誒  徹頭徹尾無視我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下的話就能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我有點必須做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能看到學美同學腦海中的影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡  有著我們學園的學生所唯獨做不到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那個答案就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天的營業就此結束  歡迎再次使用）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是理事長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:25.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（夏天結束  完成  去游泳池放煙火）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑也下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己還在做著那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是夢  而會一直繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得特別高興！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話  『戰鬥吧聖櫻學生會！』
